[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating class registration**\n\nI’m thinking about how, in the native image, a class is referenced by class literal in `getName`, making it accessible. I wonder if registration requires a `condition`. It seems that the `condition` type is indeed linked to the active class when tests call it, which is good. The top-level test class gets loaded by JUnit. I could also consider using `allDeclaredFields` but I prefer to be precise. Combining the constructor and fields into one class might simplify things.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06906b8301e934310169f55ce7b3208192af813dce82e95519\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9Vz7OZ9N4HlW5o9NqCtEvUo3iqxX8yrpVEVtjt5JX6rrTPJed-0hMMt8IwqZaN6YDOdVpgLsgTXtGuibEoQQvtWhWoiQp2Zz--uWTQESUWBduhg-RNcMFfgP218Q-K4ShgrNnDEhswblb5QSLxLcFFv93NZ1kol1WuHgGSGmJRQCRLRZEg5DsdLlWg8phri78ZIXsONqd4V-vQb_BkabS1QeHHrL-grb9-7NvR03Q5pKSP2MX6nSwv_x0Z33XwKDVzBv9ZYGFc9QUNi19-QxyxnEeIv2FskC4IwtjAUCG34hyaagW-fHTjXUnVG1OuVH8LEmxbZj2w4sC3Zylzz8sozIBVqE2AxlNGkGhjQ6vdtITgnrebaw7U5W5wl64sasxYfg29oT5JFGgi0SjAHXNVXl8_7Knj4CoHYDckJs6jRanEXw12zzy5BHPcMdzTzNkCzN4gPJhjG-eLVTCUxWDd88x7WsWrdS-xmBFfpXKWfngcFsT7R8CET6BODCUvKSuGmL37p4tKe1skS2CjtNAcixT_V12iU8RcSM3qaT8tstm7X24P6uDmgDIO2S5VWTXOi8V4oV5HMwc1zJnNIGV9mxhtu6YYV8HaoohDrKNAnYZe0K4Nr2lLX1pUuJ5XktOY_kdHeq0Ol0KV06aIwGjzilxJTVD9VAp17ZIfyC7IMEU5F0QvDBUKXuQ4bUvqJ94ITs26D2Ezw3NLflxcZtCx9mpt5Z9eH9XUx552oww6ueUMUtgS7jQVziGVfCgpAmYwVkdR4iHaEtirZomY1kmDVq8ccX3jBF7aQIi9-PE-MXG_jUbRul9YB16BTUeocUOP3NgOBfFV0Tv1eOQVQ8X43nmc4z_HjVOy-Ay3chQ_7prE1Q0NtabBQtUsxN841IC5VWK6kl5dFd_r5JIHAytQkmUJiucnVZ0CdsZwZ7eENnafXh4X7Go_OfAraWp6JfOtM0vEhIzmV2UkZKHYJYYcILfqQWBMWksll2AhpZEqslwTBIHO8M3FLd1lVuT4XNeIYEGKxhYLa7IB0jL2XUfNTkW0yJ2Fqic_lb1WpLl6msU0oi-rxH8xrgRiubNR6OkH9UVs4ubX04trJwWWujvcKd3E0ve9rN_eHpXdaX87QETX0ALfTh47x7DYH3b4IPYJW0vU4DEfLDKY0MgYZsPOvI2yey3oQnAubjNAORdJxzGn_b6V57vnc8Ss-Kag-NTST6pLL9PJ4FetROH-